”Alexa, ask garden journal to add a cucumber”
”Alexa, ask garden journal to list my harvest”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: garden journal
des: Keep track of your current vegetable garden harvest. Wouldn't it be nice to easily keep track of how many tomatoes, cucumbers, and peppers that your garden has produced this season? Now you can without having to pull out your phone and navigate an overly complicated interface. Just tell the Garden Journal skill what you've harvested and it will keep track for you. You also have the ability to remove and or clear all records.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
